# Chef Fundamentals Series

Join Chef Technical Community Director [Nathen Harvey](http://twitter.com/nathenharvey) as he covers the fundamentals of using Chef in this video series.

Each one-hour session includes hands-on labs and is followed by a Q &amp; A session.

  * Part 1 - [Overview of Chef][spring-fund-week-1]
  * Part 2 - [Node setup, resources &amp; recipes][spring-fund-week-2]
  * Part 3 - [Working with the node object and roles][spring-fund-week-3]
  * Part 4 - [Common configuration data with data bags][spring-fund-week-4]
  * Part 5 - [Using environments and knife-ec2][spring-fund-week-5]
  * Part 6 - [Community cookbooks and further resources][spring-fund-week-6]

